casebody.data:
First Department,

November, 1962

(November 1, 1962) Katie Pierri et al., Respondents, v. City of New York et al., Defendants, and Samuel J. Pierri, Appellant. Tri-Boro Asphalt Corp., Third-Party Plaintiff, v. Consolidated Telegraph and Electrical Subway Co., Third-Party Defendant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs to the respondents. No opinion. Concur — Rabin, J. P., Valente, McNally, Eager and Steuer, JJ. [31 Mise 2d 96.]
